\f1\b0\fs24 \uc0\u8232 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf3 \super 27\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub \'93But to you who are listening I say: Love your enemies, do good to those who hate you,
\f2\b\fs18 \super 28\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub bless those who curse you, pray for those who mistreat you.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 29\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub If someone slaps you on one cheek, turn to them the other also. If someone takes your coat, do not withhold your shirt from them.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 30\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Give to everyone who asks you, and if anyone takes what belongs to you, do not demand it back.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 31\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Do to others as you would have them do to you.\
\
\

\f2\b\fs18 \super 32\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub \'93If you love those who love you, what credit is that to you?\'a0Even sinners love those who love them.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 33\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub And if you do good to those who are good to you, what credit is that to you? Even sinners do that.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 34\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub And if you lend to those from whom you expect repayment, what credit is that to you?\'a0Even sinners lend to sinners, expecting to be repaid in full.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 35\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub But love your enemies, do good to them,\'a0and lend to them without expecting to get anything back. Then your reward will be great, and you will be children\'a0of the Most High,\'a0because he is kind to the ungrateful and wicked.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 36\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Be merciful,\'a0just as your Father\'a0is merciful.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

